data.description: Property offers a spacious & updated living space plus a SHOP. On a large .27 acre corner lot. Upgrades include many of the systems: newer hot water heater, AC unit, updated duct work & more, ext paint & more, list available! There is a 17x26 ft shop with a loft for storage. Inside the house, you will find that it has been thoughtfully updated throughout feat 4 bed 2 bath. This home is well situated for all of your needs. Plenty of storage including a storage shed and a 12x30 RV Cover. Call today!
